{"word":"ἄσκεπτος","slug":"ἄσκεπτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄσκεπτος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σκοπέω'><el>σκοπέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>inconsiderate, unreflecting</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-τως</el>, <i>inconsiderately</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>unconsidered, unobserved</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}